y\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winning a medal in front of Buckingham Palace, that was my big motivation.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"Buckingham Palace\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"my big motivation\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going 'would not it be great', an Irish man going over, racing in front of Buckingham Palace and waving to the Queen with an Olympic medal around your neck and Irish flags everywhere.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998110335441931, \"rank\": 8.199572903593262e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9998110335441931, \"rank\": 8.199572903593262e-05, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"Buckingham Palace\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the Queen\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"your neck\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Mall was amazing.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Mall\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I finished fourth in the race and the time that I did that day would have won at every other Olympic Games, or it wou